avene mine \u2013 at det m\u00e5 v\u00e6re et definitivt nedfelt dokument, som forteller om samarbeidet mellom de to eierne, sier Wed\u00f8."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "pluss"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "pluss|sport"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "6da61703bca80bb84c9f6b80105a71ad65679763f2aa7fe8e64a009cb4d30a42"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-05-01T05:57:45.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "I november ga legene Hans J\u00f8rgen Wed\u00f8 beskjed om at han snart skal d\u00f8. Da startet jakten p\u00e5 den perfekte kj\u00f8peren av livsverket hans."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/pluss/sport/article10714661.ece/31ir55/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Wedoe_0033.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/370854f68318a61b50b69a4de21172ffdead29bd.jpg?598063eb"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Sikrer hjertebarnet f\u00f8r han d\u00f8r -adressa.no", "Kort tid igjen", "\u2013 Kunne f\u00e5tt ti mill. mer"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "370854f68318a61b50b69a4de21172ffdead29bd"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["pluss", "eadressa", "ukeadressa", "digitalt", "arkiv", "fordeler"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "pluss,eadressa,ukeadressa,digitalt,arkiv,fordeler"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["pluss", "sport"]}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": "gran\u00e5sen utvikling as"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["leve", "bygget", "toppidrettssenteret", "millioner kroner"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["sinsenkrysset", "bolig", "hans j\u00f8rgen wed\u00f8", "sparebank 1", "alf-egil bogen og p\u00e5l pettersen berg", "toppidrettssenteret", "alf-egil", "hans j\u00f8rgen"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["europa", "hitra", "trondheim", "lofoten", "midt-norge", "bergen"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"fie